Package com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.core.domain

Contains domain classes for SNOMED CT.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConceptEnum
    Enumerations implementing this interface can provide a SNOMED CT concept identifier for each value.
    DefinitionStatusProvider
    Holds a SNOMED CT concept's definition status.
    IdGenerationStrategy
    Implementations allow clients to generate component identifiers conforming to the specified constraints.
    ISnomedExportConfiguration
    Represents the configuration object used by a SNOMED CT RF2 Export implementation.
    ISnomedImportConfiguration
    Represents the configuration object used by a SNOMED CT RF2 Importer implementation.
    ISnomedRF2Configuration
    Common super interface for RF2 based import-export configurations.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CharacteristicTypePredicates
    Predicates regarding CharacteristicTypes.
    CharacteristicTypePredicates.CharacteristicTypeByIdPredicate
    Predicate for CharacteristicType IDs.
    CharacteristicTypePredicates.CharacteristicTypeIComponentPredicate
    Predicate for CharacteristicType IComponents
    ConstantIdStrategy  
    NamespaceIdStrategy  
    SnomedComponent
    Holds common properties of SNOMED CT components.
    SnomedConcept
    Represents a SNOMED CT concept.
    SnomedConcept.Expand
    Enumerates expandable property keys.
    SnomedConcepts
    A page-able collection of SNOMED CT concepts.
    SnomedCoreComponent  
    SnomedDescription
    Represents a SNOMED CT description.
    SnomedDescriptions  
    SnomedRelationship
    Represents a SNOMED CT relationship.
    SnomedRelationships  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Acceptability
    Enumerates allowed acceptability values and maps them to concept identifiers.
    AssociationType
    Enumerates known historical association reference sets and their corresponding identifier concepts.
    CaseSignificance
    Enumerates allowed description case significance values and their SNOMED CT concept counterparts.
    CharacteristicType
    Enumerates allowed relationship characteristic types and their corresponding concept identifiers.
    DefinitionStatus
    Enumerates allowed concept definition status values and their corresponding concept identifiers.
    DescriptionInactivationIndicator
    Enumeration to specify the reason of the inactivation of SNOMED CT descriptions.
    InactivationIndicator
    Enumeration to specify the reason of the inactivation of SNOMED CT concepts.
    ISnomedImportConfiguration.ImportStatus
    Enumerates possible values for the state of an RF2 import process.
    RelationshipModifier
    Enumerates allowed relationship modifiers and maps them to concept identifiers.
    RelationshipRefinability
    Enumerates allowed relationship refinability values and maps them to concept identifiers.
    Rf2ReleaseType
    Enumerates available RF2 release formats for the SNOMED CT ontology.
    SubclassDefinitionStatus
    Enumerates assertions about direct subclasses.
